这个问题的根源在于v2rayN把xray的config.json转换成sing-box的配置时，发生格式错误。经过反复测试，正确的ss+ws+tls节点的配置应为：
`            {
            "domain_strategy":"",
            "method":"chacha20-ietf-poly1305",
            "password":"xxxxx",
            "plugin":"v2ray-plugin",
            "plugin_opts":"tls;host=vps.com;mux=0",
            "server":"vps.com",
            "server_port":443,
            "tag":"proxy",
            "type":"shadowsocks",
            "udp_over_tcp":false
}`
而v2rayN生成的格式为：
`    {
      "type": "shadowsocks",
      "tag": "proxy",
      "server": "vps.com",
      "server_port": 443,
      "method": "chacha20-ietf-poly1305",
      "password": "xxxxx",
      "tls": {
        "enabled": true,
        "server_name": "vps.com",
        "insecure": false,
        "utls": {
          "enabled": true,
          "fingerprint": "chrome"
        }
      },
      "transport": {
        "type": "ws",
        "path": "/",
        "headers": {
          "Host": "vps.com"
        }
      }
    }`
很明显，是错误的格式，会导致节点使用sing-box内核或使用sing-box内核的TUN模式时无法连接。这确实是bug

